{"role": "assistant", "content": "好的！挑战更难的题目：\n\n---\n\n**题目：**\n\n计算以下多项式运算：\n\n$$\\frac{(x^4 - 2x^3 + 3x^2 - 4x + 5)(x^3 + x^2 - 2x + 3)}{(x - 1)(x + 2)}$$\n\n**要求：**\n1. 先进行多项式乘法\n2. 再进行多项式除法（分解因式）\n3. 最后化简结果\n\n---\n\n**答案：**\n\n**第一步：多项式乘法**\n\n$$\n\\begin{aligned}\n(x^4 - 2x^3 + 3x^2 - 4x + 5)(x^3 + x^2 - 2x + 3) &= x^4(x^3 + x^2 - 2x + 3) - 2x^3(x^3 + x^2 - 2x + 3) \\\\\n&\\quad + 3x^2(x^3 + x^2 - 2x + 3) - 4x(x^3 + x^2 - 2x + 3) + 5(x^3 + x^2 - 2x + 3) \\\\\n&= x^7 + x^6 - 2x^5 + 3x^4 - 2x^6 - 2x^5 + 4x^4 - 6x^3 + 3x^5 + 3x^4 - 6x^3 + 9x^2 \\\\\n&\\quad - 4x^4 - 4x^3 + 8x^2 - 12x + 5x^3 + 5x^2 - 10x + 15 \\\\\n&= x^7 + (x^6 - 2x^6) + (-2x^5 - 2x^5 + 3x^5) + (3x^4 + 4x^4 + 3x^4 - 4x^4) \\\\\n&\\quad + (-6x^3 - 6x^3 - 4x^3 + 5x^3) + (9x^2 + 8x^2 + 5x^2) + (-12x - 10x) + 15 \\\\\n&= x^7 - x^6 - x^5 + 6x^4 - 11x^3 + 22x^2 - 22x + 15\n\\end{aligned}\n$$\n\n**第二步：多项式除法**\n\n$$\n\\frac{x^7 - x^6 - x^5 + 6x^4 - 11x^3 + 22x^2 - 22x + 15}{(x - 1)(x + 2)} = \\frac{x^7 - x^6 - x^5 + 6x^4 - 11x^3 + 22x^2 - 22x + 15}{x^2 + x - 2}\n$$\n\n使用长除法：\n\n$$\n\\begin{array}{r|rrrrrrr}\nx^2 + x - 2 & x^7 & -x^6 & -x^5 & +6x^4 & -11x^3 & +22x^2 & -22x & +15 \\\\\n\\hline\n& x^5 & -2x^4 & +3x^3 & -3x^2 & +6x & -12 & -3 \\\\\n\\end{array}\n$$\n\n**最终答案：**\n\n$$x^5 - 2x^4 + 3x^3 - 3x^2 + 6x - 12 - \\frac{3}{x^2 + x - 2}$$\n\n---\n\n**或者进一步分解：**\n\n$$x^5 - 2x^4 + 3x^3 - 3x^2 + 6x - 12 - \\frac{3}{(x - 1)(x + 2)}$$\n\n---\n\n怎么样？这个题目涉及：\n- 7次多项式乘法\n- 2次多项式除法\n- 因式分解\n\n需要我详细解释某个步骤吗？ 😊", "timestamp": "2026-03-12T19:41:24.017521"}
